<taxonomicName authorityName="Hutterer" authorityYear="1983" box="[2046,2215,1523,1552]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Crocidura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="129" pageNumber="538" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="grandiceps">C. grandiceps</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Bocage" baseAuthorityYear="1887" box="[2231,2485,1523,1552]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Crocidura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="129" pageNumber="526" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="thomensis">Crocidura thomensis</taxonomicName>
might also be closely related to C. fingui. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
